&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Prioritize safety at all times and comply with OSHA guidelines.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Communicate clearly and professionally with customers, team members, and office staff.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Utilize tools and software (like ServiceTitan) to track jobs and update progress.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
